screen_desc: The screenshot displays a pizza menu item titled "Supreme," which has a rating of 89% based on 19 reviews. The description lists the ingredients: ham, salami, Spanish onions, fresh button mushrooms, fresh capsicum, pineapple, Kalamata olives, and mozzarella, with anchovies as an optional addition. Below the description, there is a section for selecting the pizza size, with options including 9", 12", 12" Gluten-Free, 15", and 18", each with an additional cost. The base price for the Supreme pizza is A$14.95, and there is a prominent button to "Add Item."
